    content: `# Best AI Writing Tools 2026: ChatGPT vs Jasper vs Claude Compared

The AI writing market has reached $4.8 billion in 2026 (Gartner), and choosing the right tool can save your team 20+ hours per week. I spent three months testing 10 leading platforms to bring you this detailed comparison.

## At a Glance: Top AI Writing Tools Compared

| Platform | Rating | Best For | Starting Price |
